{"tid":2159332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據了解全民自願檢測同時採集鼻腔及咽喉拭子樣本","createTime":"2020-08-16T09:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T11:39:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad06e55b8d2d38c3b2f59037e47103d87ad10ef","tid":2159332,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:12:07.000Z","msg":"政府籌備的全民自願檢測將會招募私家醫生、牙醫及護士等協助。據了解，目標希望徵集逾二千人，西醫工會已收到邀請信。會長楊超發預計，會有幾百名醫生參加。據了解，政府傾向同時採集鼻腔及咽喉拭子樣本，而非鼻咽拭子樣本。<br />\n<br />\n政府正籌備全民自願檢測計劃。據了解，政府傾向同時採集市民的鼻腔及咽喉拭子樣本，而非鼻咽拭子樣本，同時由醫護人員去做，預計招募逾二千醫護幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n西醫工會已收到食物及衞生局的邀請信，指全民自願檢測將會在本月底展開，為期十四天。<br />\n<br />\n政府會在全港十八區設抽取樣本站，每個站有總管、副總管及其他成員，分別可獲每小時八百、六百及三百元車馬費，參與的醫護都會有外科口罩和手套等合適的防護裝備。<br />\n<br />\n西醫工會會長楊超發預計，有幾百名醫生願意參與計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=401932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401932&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJB5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=1effdca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D401932&h=f331d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=401932</a>"},{"pid":"6dfa25c7b1e2701217d578846c752670d2c426f6","tid":2159332,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:17:40.000Z","msg":"篤到有DNA為止"},{"pid":"e368dbbf0e4975139ac33e1a19ab979c0892dbcd","tid":2159332,"uid":2475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"去做既都係幫兇"},{"pid":"93b826c70c834c6d6ded67885d29c77fdeace59b","tid":2159332,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"（正視聽）戴口罩、暫停聚集係值得鼓勵，但係強制戴口罩on9惡法同限聚惡法係一定要反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2159357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2159357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"18f3a4ed41bc2cdf01d7d5bc7a60c1c4084646c0","tid":2159332,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"藍店連鎖「唔做既唔比返工」<br />\n已經唔係「自願」檢測"},{"pid":"0401b9b691370d110c37ce5ba8a36172a9a5e21a","tid":2159332,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18f3a4ed41bc2cdf01d7d5bc7a60c1c4084646c0","tid":2159332,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"藍店連鎖「唔做既唔比返工」<br />\n已經唔係「自願」檢測"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"驗完再中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}